# Usage

## Subscriptions

\


```
|--------subscription-------------------------------------------->
start             (subscription duration)                end or inf
#
|-----------------------------|---------------------------|------>
charge   (charge period)    charge                      charge
#
|------------------------------x
quota   (quota lifetime)       quota burned
#
(quota recharge period) |------------------------------x
#
(quota recharge period) (quota recharge period) |----------------->
```

